A sleek single-wheeled personal mobility device with a futuristic spherical wheel design, shown mid-motion on a rain-slicked Singapore street at dusk. Neon pink and electric blue lights reflect off wet pavement, casting dramatic glows on the compact foldable frame. The scene captures the device from a low dynamic angle, emphasizing its minimalist engineering against a backdrop of towering cyberpunk architecture with holographic advertisements and steam rising from street vents. The wheel glows with an inner amber light as it balances impossibly, surrounded by the blur of passing hovercars and pedestrians in translucent rain gear. Moody atmosphere with deep shadows and saturated accent colors in cyan, magenta, and golden yellow.
